name: Ready to Paint
description: It’s amazing to me that human beings are made of the same material as stars. As I create art pieces, it feels like I’m dreaming among the stars, manipulating color and shapes, miraculously traveling in a world filled with color and infinite possibilities. "Ready to Paint" is featured in iDENTITY | 01 | Bit.Shes Summer 2021 Collection. All proceeds from this piece go to charity. Check out bitshes.com for more info!
